quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,“Ndikulumbira nyenyezi pamene zikulowa
  53,2,“Sadasokere m’bale wanu (Mtumiki panjira ya choonadi) ndipo sadakhulupirire zonama
  53,3,“Ndipo sayankhula zofuna za mtima wake
  53,4,"“Iyoyi (Qur’an imene akuinena), sichina, koma ndichivumbulutso chovumbulutsidwa"
  53,5,“Adamphunzitsa (chivumbulutsochi) (Jibril) wanyonga zambiri
  53,6,“Wanzeru zakuya; ndipo adakhazikika (m’maonekedwe ake)
  53,7,“Ali m’chizimezime kumwamba
  53,8,"“Kenako (Jibril) adamuyandikira (Mtumiki {s.a.w}) ndikuonjezera kumuyandikira"
  53,9,"“(Kumuyandikira kwake) kudali ngati (mpata wa) nsonga ziwiri za uta, kapena kuyandikira kuposa apo"
  53,10,“(Choncho Jibril) adavumbulutsira kapolo wake (wa Allah) zimene adazivumbulutsa
  53,11,“Sudaname mtima (wa Mtumiki) pazimene adaziona
  53,12,“Kodi mukutsutsana naye (Mthenga wa Allah) pazimene adaziona
  53,13,“Ndipo ndithu adamuona (Jibril) m’kuona kachiwiri mkaonekedwe kake
  53,14,“Pa ‘Sidratil Muntaha’ (mtengo wamasawu pothera zinthu zonse)
  53,15,"“Pafupi pake pali Janatu Ma’awa, (munda wokhalamo)"
  53,16,“Pomwe chophimba chidaphimba msawuwo
  53,17,“Maso ake sadaphonye kapena kupyola malire (oikidwa)
  53,18,"“Ndithu (Mneneri Muhammad {s.a.w}) adaona zina mwa zizindikiro zikuluzikulu za Mbuye wake (zosonyeza mphamvu Zake)"
  53,19,“Kodi mwamuona Laat ndi Uzza
  53,20,"“Ndi Manata; (fano lanu) lina lachitatu, (kuti iwowa ndi milungu)"
  53,21,"“Kodi mwadzisankhira ana aamuna (kukhala anu), ndi aakazi nkukhala a Iye (Allah)"
  53,22,“Choncho kugawa kumeneko nkopanda chilungamo (pompatsa Allah zimene mumazida)
  53,23,"“Sali (mafanowo) chilichonse koma ndi maina basi omwe mudawatcha inu ndi makolo anu, (molingana ndi zilakolako zanu zachabe); Allah sadatsitse umboni pazimenezo (wotsimikiza pamawu anuwo). Sakutsatira koma zoganizira basi ndi zimene ikufuna mitima (yawo yopotoka). Ndithu chidawadzera chiongoko kuchokera kwa Mbuye wawo (chomwe m’kati mwake mudali kuongoka kwawo akadachitsatira)"
  53,24,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti adzapeza chilichonse chimene akuchilakalaka
  53,25,“Moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro ndi wadziko lapansi ngwa Allah Yekha
  53,26,“Ndipo kuli angelo ambiri kumwamba omwe kuchondelera kwawo sikungathandize china chilichonse pokhapokha Allah ataloleza kwa amene wamfuna ndi kumuyanja
  53,27,"“Ndithu amene sakhulupirira za (Moyo wa) tsiku lachimaliziro, amawatcha angelo kuti ndiakazi"
  53,28,“Ndipo alibe kudziwa kulikonse pa zimenezo sakutsata china koma maganizo. Ndipo ndithu kuganizira sikuthandiza chilichonse pofuna kupeza choonadi
  53,29,“Choncho apewe (osakhulupirirawa) amene anyozera chikumbutso Chathu (Qur’an); ndipo palibe chimene akufuna koma moyo wa padziko lapansi basi
  53,30,“Zimenezo ndiwo mapeto a kudziwa kwawo. Ndithu Mbuye wako Ngodziwa kwambiri za amene akusokera njira Yake ndiponso akudziwa bwino za yemwe wawongoka
  53,31,"“Ndipo zonse za kumwamba ndi zadziko lapansi nza Allah Yekha, (pozilenga ndi kuziyang’anira), kuti adzawalipire amene adaipitsa pa zimene adachita ndi kutinso adzawalipire zabwino amene adachita zabwino"
  53,32,"“Amene akuwapewa machimo akuluakulu ndi zadama, kupatula timachimo tating’onoting’ono (timene Allah amatikhululuka); ndithu Mbuye wako ndiwokhululuka kwakukulu. Iye akudziwa chikhalidwe chanu kuyambira pomwe adakulengani kuchokera m’nthaka ndi pamene inu mudali makanda m’mimba mwa amayi anu (mosinthasintha; mosiyanasiyana). Choncho musadzitame nokha kuyera mtima; Iye Ngodziwa kwambiri za yemwe akumuopa (Allah)"
  53,33,“Kodi wamuona yemwe wadzipatula (pakusiya kutsatira choonadi)
  53,34,“Ndipo wapereka (chuma) chochepa nasiyanso kuperekako
  53,35,"“Kodi akudziwa zamseri, kotero kuti akuziwona (zomwe wadza nazo (Mtumiki {s.a.w) kuti sizoona"
  53,36,“Kapena sadauzidwe zomwe zidali m’mabuku a Mûsa
  53,37,“Ndi Ibrahim amene adakwaniritsa (lonjezo la Allah)
  53,38,“Kuti mzimu wamachimo sungasenze machimo a mzimu wina
  53,39,“Ndi kutinso munthu sakalipidwa koma zimene adachita
  53,40,“Ndipo ndithu ntchito zake zidzaonekera
  53,41,“Kenako (munthu) adzalipidwa malipiro okwanira (pa ntchito zake zimene amachita)
  53,42,“Ndipo ndithu kwa Mbuye wako yekha ndiwo malekezero (a chilichonse)
  53,43,“Ndithu Iye ndiAmene amapereka chisangalalo ndi zoliritsa
  53,44,“Ndipo Iye yekha ndi Amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene adalenga mitundu iwiri: chachimuna ndi chachikazi, (anthu ndi zamoyo zina)"
  53,46,“Kuchokera m’mbewu ya moyo pamene imafwamphukira (m’chiberekero)
  53,47,“Ndipo ndithu ndi udindo Wake kuukitsa kwina (pambuyo pa imfa)
  53,48,“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene amapatsa chokwanira ndipo ndi amene amapatsa chosunga
  53,49,“Ndipo ndithu Iye ndi Mbuye wa nyenyezi yotchedwa Shiira
  53,50,“Ndipo Iye ndi amene adaononga Âdi oyamba; (anthu a Mneneri Hûd)
  53,51,“Ndi Samudu; (anthu a Mneneri Swaleh;) choncho sadasiye (ndi mmodzi yemwe wa iwo)
  53,52,"“Ndipo (adawaononganso) anthu a Nuh, kale (asadaononge Âdi ndi Samudu). Ndithu iwo adali osalungama ndi olumpha malire kwambiri (kuposa Âdi ndi Samudu)"
  53,53,"“Ndi midzi yotembenuzidwa kumwamba kukhala pansi, pansi kukhala kumwamba, (ya anthu a Luti) adaigwetsa"
  53,54,“Tero chidaivindikira (midziyo) chomwe chidaivindikira (chilango)
  53,55,“Kodi ndimtendere uti (mumtendere) wa Mbuye wako umene ukuukaikira
  53,56,“Uyu (Mtumiki) ndimchenjezi mwa achenjezi oyamba (amene adachenjezedwa nawo anthu a mibadwo yakale)
  53,57,“Chayandikira choyandikira (Qiyâma)
  53,58,“Palibe amene angachionetse koma Allah Yekha
  53,59,“Kodi mukuidabwa nkhaniyi (ya Qur’an moikana)
  53,60,“Mungoseka (mwachipongwe) ndipo simukulira (pamene mukuimva monga momwe akuchitira okhulupirira)
  53,61,“Ndipo mukunyozera
  53,62,“Mlambireni ndi kumpembedza Allah (amene wavumbulutsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chiongoko cha anthu)